Tammy, you have a visitor.

35:05.437 --> 35:08.706
You have pay-per-view in here?

35:08.774 --> 35:10.474
Kara.

35:10.509 --> 35:11.643
You've come to gloat.

35:11.710 --> 35:13.044
I've come to tell you

35:13.078 --> 35:15.046
that you'd better hurry up
and get back in the octagon.

35:16.248 --> 35:17.881
[sighs] It could be awhile.

35:17.916 --> 35:20.451
Yeah, well...

35:20.485 --> 35:22.986
until then, how about you train me?

35:23.021 --> 35:25.022
What about Noelle?

35:25.090 --> 35:27.425
I had to let her go.

35:27.492 --> 35:28.859
She's a bit of a heel.

35:28.893 --> 35:30.727
[chuckles]

35:30.762 --> 35:32.563
So it's safe to leave you two alone awhile?

35:33.965 --> 35:35.265
Yeah.

35:36.568 --> 35:38.134
Hey.

35:39.403 --> 35:40.871
Thanks.

