Do you have something you'd like to tell me?

36:10.634 --> 36:11.567
No.

36:11.635 --> 36:12.969
Dr. Larouche drove you home.

36:13.003 --> 36:15.004
Yeah.

36:15.038 --> 36:19.709
I snuck out, came back.

36:19.743 --> 36:21.243
Is leila up yet?

36:29.819 --> 36:32.187
What do you say we let her
