Giselle, have you been
living here this whole time?

36:59.214 --> 37:00.681
No.

37:02.851 --> 37:04.519
Just the past two days.

37:09.358 --> 37:10.891
You can't sleep here.

37:20.535 --> 37:22.736
[weakly] Mom.

37:22.771 --> 37:25.539
Yeah, pet. I'm here. I'm right here.

37:28.076 --> 37:29.409
I'm sorry.

37:31.579 --> 37:32.646
No.

37:33.681 --> 37:37.817
No, no. <i>I</i> am.

37:37.885 --> 37:41.188
[sighs] Sweetheart, I...

37:41.255 --> 37:44.558
