38:10.550 --> 38:11.783
Molly.

38:11.818 --> 38:14.353
Do you know how hard it is
being your daughter?

38:14.421 --> 38:18.090
You're smart. You're beautiful.

38:18.124 --> 38:19.290
So are you.

38:19.358 --> 38:21.593
And you go to work
